eNCA's Masego Rahlaga reports. Courtesy of #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The Hawks has confirmed it's investigating a case of fraud in relation to the so-called Heritage Fund. ANC veteran Tokyo Sexwale has dug in his heels on the authenticity of the fund. READ: Heritage Fund | Sexwale hits back at critics He detailed communication with President Cyril Ramaphosa and Finance Minister Tito Mboweni informing them of a rot within the Reserve Bank. Sexwale claims billions meant for the poor have been stolen. * eNCA's Masego Rahlaga reports.